Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.68,0:02:31.20,op cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}在回憶裏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:37.05,op cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}想哭的時候 想見的時候
